;A Brand New Tiles Experience
Ina novischma experientscha cun las Plattinas


;With Enhanced Tiles and Directory Tiles, Firefox provides users easy access to interesting, relevant content, whether it’s the sites they visit most or new sites for them to discover.
Cun las Plattinas scortas e las Plattinas da reclama porscha Firefox als utilisaders in simpel access a cuntegn interessant e relevant – i sa tracta tant da las paginas ch'els visitan il pli savens sco era da paginas novas ch'els pon scuvrir.


;What are Tiles?
Tge èn las Plattinas?


;When you open a new tab in Firefox, you see several rectangles that link to different websites.
Sche ti avras in nov tab en Firefox, vesas ti divers rectanguls che mainan a differentas paginas d'internet.


;Some people call them squares, windows or bookmarks; we call them Tiles.
Tscherta glieud las numna fanestras u segnapaginas, nus las numnain «plattinas».


;What are Enhanced Tiles?
Tge èn las Plattinas scortas?


;Existing Firefox users will be offered a set of Enhanced Tiles based on their browsing history.
Utilisaders che dovran gia daditg Firefox vegnan a vesair ina retscha da Plattinas scortas che sa basan sin lur cronologia da navigaziun.


;The Enhanced versions replace the default screenshot with a better image and are displayed only for sites that the user has visited.
Las versiuns scortas remplazzan il maletg dal visur da standard cun in meglier maletg e mussan mo paginas che l'utilisader ha gia visità.


;The improved image is supplied by the site or partner and can include a logo plus a rollover image.
Quest meglier maletg vegn mess a disposiziun da la website u dal partenari e po cumpigliar in logo plus in maletg che vegn mussà sch'il punctader da la mieur vegn posiziunà sin la Plattina.


;If you frequent Amazon.com, for example, you might see the Amazon logo or icon, instead of a screenshot.
Sche ti visitas per exempel Amazon.com, vesas ti eventualmain en futur in logo dad Amazon enstagl dad in maletg dal visur da la pagina dad Amazon.


;What are Directory Tiles?
Tge èn Plattinas da reclama?


;New Firefox users are initially given a set of Directory Tiles as suggestions for sites that may be of interest to them.
Novs utilisaders da Firefox vesan l'entschatta ina schelta da Plattinas da reclama sco propostas per paginas ch'als pudessan interessar.


;Instead of displaying a blank set of Tiles, Firefox shows content from Mozilla and some Mozilla partners.
Enstagl da mussar ina retscha da Plattinas vidas mussa Firefox cuntegn da Mozilla e da tscherts partenaris da Mozilla.


;All partner content is marked as “sponsored” and users have complete control to edit or remove any Tile.
L'entir cuntegn da partenaris è marcà sco „sponsurà“ ed ils utilisaders pon adina modifitgar u allontanar mintga Plattina.


;Respects your privacy
Cun respectar la protecziun da datas


;As with all Mozilla products, Tiles provide users with extensive control over their personal data.
Sco mintga product da Mozilla, porschan las Plattinas la pussaivladad als utilisaders da controllar cumplainamain lur datas persunalas.


;Data collection is limited to the aggregate number of impressions, clicks and Tile placement.
Las unicas datas che vegnan rimnadas pertutgan il dumber total da visitas dad ina pagina, ils clics ed igl arranschament da las Plattinas.


;Nothing is ever personally identifiable. In other words, we don’t know who clicks on what.
Nagut da quai pon ins attribuir ad ina persuna. Cun auters pleds: Nus na savain betg tgi che clicca sin tge.


;We just know the total number of views and clicks an individual Tile receives. This helps us deliver the most interesting and relevant content.
Nus enconuschain mo il dumber total da visitas e clics ch'ina singula Plattina ha. Quai ans gida da porscher il cuntegn pli interessant e relevant.


;You can deactivate click and impression tracking by clicking on the gear icon on the top right corner of the new tab page, and selecting Classic to show only unenhanced History Tiles or Blank mode.
Ti pos deactivar la registraziun da las visitas ed ils clics cun cliccar sin la roda dentada en il chantun sura a dretga da la pagina dal nov tab. Là èsi da tscherner Classic per mo mussar Plattinas senza il modus scort u il modus vid.


;Frequently Asked Questions
Dumondas frequentas


;Are you tracking users now?
Persequitais vus ussa ils utilisaders?


;We only collect data from the New Tab page in aggregate form, meaning no data is personally identifiable.
Nus rimnain mo datas da la pagina mussada sin in nov tab e quai en furma accumulada. Quai vul dir ch'igl è impussibel dad attribuir las datas a singulas persunas.


;What data is being collected?
Tge datas vegnan rimnadas?


;Aggregate data from the New Tab page includes impressions, clicks and tile placement.
Las datas accumuladas da la pagina mussada sin in nov tab includa las visitas, ils clics ed igl arranschament da las Plattinas.


;What data is collected when I opt out?
Tge datas vegnan rimnadas sche jau deactivesch la funcziun?


;No data is collected when a user chooses to opt out of the enhanced Tiles experience.
Sch'in utilisader decida da deactivar la funcziun da las Plattinas scortas na vegnan naginas datas rimnadas.


